com.example.einarsandberg.projekt

Class AccountParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.einarsandberg.projekt.AccountParameter

  • public class AccountParameter
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains an account parameter with it's input feedback visualization method, as well as the algorithm, if the user has specified that he/she wants to use input feedback. An account consists of a list of AccountParameter.
